    "Ms are the core of our framework LLM-RS, and largely determine the performance of LLMs as recommender systems [44,52,86,87].",
    "Therefore, it is worth exploring how to choose a suitable LLM as the foundation for recommendation.",
    "In this section, we compare the differences between LLMs and traditional models on the recommendation performance, discuss how the different properties and tuning strategies of LLMs affect the recommendation results, present the limitations of LLMs as recommenders, and draw empirical conclusions through systematic experiments.",
    "Classification of LLMsIn this paper, we consider language models that have a size larger that one billion as LLMs.",
    "In line with existing researches [63,77,156,184,185], LLMs can be categorized into different classes from several perspectives."
